WEBVTT

01:30.870 --> 01:35.100
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.840 --> 01:38.229
[2006]

01:38.150 --> 01:38.880
Xia Xiaolan,

01:38.920 --> 01:40.310
you're not allowed to
go out with him anymore!

01:40.310 --> 01:42.039
You're not worthy of him at all!

01:42.150 --> 01:42.759
Who?

01:42.840 --> 01:44.039
Don't play dumb here!

01:44.200 --> 01:46.200
I saw everything during the New Year!

01:46.200 --> 01:47.710
You'd better know your place!

01:47.710 --> 01:48.560
Or next time,

01:48.560 --> 01:50.200
it won't just be a verbal warning!

01:50.200 --> 01:50.600
Got it.

01:51.430 --> 01:52.070
Move!

01:55.200 --> 01:57.640
There are always obstacles
on the road to happiness.

01:57.640 --> 01:59.570
As long as you keep moving forward,

02:00.000 --> 02:01.200
no one can stop you

02:01.200 --> 02:02.400
from finding it.

02:03.400 --> 02:06.040
[Episode 28: Happiness No One Can Stop]

02:10.910 --> 02:11.400
Sir!

02:12.800 --> 02:13.260
Coming!

02:13.310 --> 02:14.590
One bowl of sampan porridge

02:14.590 --> 02:16.120
and a plate of braised meat.

02:16.230 --> 02:16.760
Alright.

02:19.240 --> 02:20.680
And a dozen oysters

02:20.800 --> 02:21.930
and a bottle of beer.

02:22.190 --> 02:23.680
A dozen oysters, one beer.

02:24.030 --> 02:24.960
Forget the beer.

02:25.240 --> 02:26.170
Two herbal teas.

02:26.240 --> 02:27.810
And one order of stir-fried rice noodles.

02:27.810 --> 02:29.410
Alright, please have a seat.

02:34.680 --> 02:35.470
Zhou Cheng?

02:35.910 --> 02:36.430
San,

02:36.840 --> 02:38.900
don't drink if you're driving later.

02:39.120 --> 02:40.079
You're here to help me

02:40.079 --> 02:41.810
deal with that bastard, right?

02:42.910 --> 02:43.360
Hello.

02:44.210 --> 02:45.540
Why didn't Ge Jian come?

02:46.710 --> 02:48.710
I'm here to ask you to go back with me.

02:50.560 --> 02:51.360
Let me ask you—

02:51.870 --> 02:52.590
if it had been Xiaolan

02:52.590 --> 02:53.920
who got beaten up today,

02:54.120 --> 02:55.430
could you just let it go?

02:55.430 --> 02:57.160
Could you take that lying down?

02:57.310 --> 02:59.000
Of course, I wouldn't let it go.

02:59.000 --> 03:00.400
But I also wouldn't be so reckless as to

03:00.400 --> 03:02.310
charge over there and pick a fight.

03:02.310 --> 03:02.710
San,

03:03.590 --> 03:04.560
fighting isn't going to

03:04.560 --> 03:05.240
solve anything right now.

03:05.240 --> 03:06.300
Alright, alright.

03:06.750 --> 03:08.630
I never liked hearing you talk like that.

03:08.630 --> 03:10.120
No matter how we solve it later,

03:10.120 --> 03:11.240
today I have to

03:11.240 --> 03:12.640
settle this score first!

03:12.910 --> 03:13.570
Zhou Cheng.

03:14.400 --> 03:16.329
It's fine if you don't want to help,

03:16.430 --> 03:17.690
but don't get in my way.

03:24.120 --> 03:25.840
The mahjong parlor is crowded at night.

03:25.840 --> 03:27.240
Do you want to wait until dawn

03:27.240 --> 03:28.190
to make your move?

03:28.190 --> 03:29.240
Or follow him home

03:29.470 --> 03:30.680
and beat him up

03:31.000 --> 03:32.200
somewhere secluded?

03:33.840 --> 03:34.470
You know

03:34.910 --> 03:36.640
that this is Ke Yixiong's turf.

03:36.870 --> 03:38.190
They have the numbers.

03:39.240 --> 03:40.440
You can't act rashly.

03:40.680 --> 03:41.280
Of course.

03:42.560 --> 03:43.400
I, Pan Baohua,

03:44.150 --> 03:45.280
am no reckless fool.

03:45.560 --> 03:47.280
Ke Yixiong has been
on the streets for so long.

03:47.280 --> 03:49.010
You think he's a reckless fool?

03:50.710 --> 03:52.570
Wouldn't he
have already thought of all this?

03:52.570 --> 03:54.680
He showed up in broad daylight,
bold as anything.

03:54.680 --> 03:56.079
What if it's a trap?

03:57.910 --> 03:58.710
You rush over,

03:58.910 --> 03:59.630
beat him up,

03:59.960 --> 04:00.680
injure him,

04:01.030 --> 04:01.840
or worse, cripple him...

04:01.840 --> 04:02.370
Alright!

04:03.710 --> 04:05.370
I know what you're getting at.

04:05.630 --> 04:06.710
I've already

04:07.030 --> 04:07.870
thought all that through

04:07.870 --> 04:09.000
on my way here.

04:10.240 --> 04:10.960
At worst,

04:11.470 --> 04:13.470
I'll just be locked up for a few days.

04:13.710 --> 04:14.590
When I get out,

04:14.870 --> 04:17.000
I'll still be a man to be reckoned with!

04:20.040 --> 04:20.970
Enjoy your food.

04:23.470 --> 04:24.800
You get to play the hero.

04:25.630 --> 04:26.960
But what about Zhenzhu?

04:28.430 --> 04:29.430
You're gambling

04:30.310 --> 04:32.310
your entire future just to help her.

04:32.390 --> 04:33.240
This will always

04:33.240 --> 04:34.390
stand between you.

04:35.310 --> 04:38.440
Then I guess you might as well
never see each other again.

04:52.480 --> 04:52.950
I...

04:55.510 --> 04:56.840
I didn't think that far.

04:58.560 --> 05:00.420
I just wanted to help Sis Zhenzhu.

05:00.510 --> 05:01.770
I wanted to avenge her!

05:02.000 --> 05:03.330
Then think about it now.

05:04.310 --> 05:05.240
Just think about

05:05.630 --> 05:06.510
how Zhenzhu is.

05:07.430 --> 05:09.560
And think about your future together.

05:17.630 --> 05:18.430
Do you still remember

05:18.430 --> 05:20.290
what your attackers looked like?

05:20.720 --> 05:21.390
I definitely can't

05:21.390 --> 05:22.560
remember all of them.

05:22.560 --> 05:23.120
But

05:23.430 --> 05:24.480
there was one

05:24.800 --> 05:26.060
with dyed yellow hair,

05:26.430 --> 05:27.160
a sharp face,

05:27.160 --> 05:27.820
and a tattoo

05:28.000 --> 05:29.630
on his arm.

05:29.630 --> 05:30.360
His name is Qiang.

05:30.360 --> 05:31.690
He was there yesterday.

05:32.240 --> 05:33.840
You remember him so clearly.

05:34.720 --> 05:36.600
I used to run a small stall

05:37.070 --> 05:38.440
at Renmin Bridge.

05:38.560 --> 05:40.750
He came around often.

05:41.070 --> 05:42.159
You know how it is—

05:42.159 --> 05:43.430
we stay alert

05:43.560 --> 05:45.070
to those types when doing business,

05:45.070 --> 05:46.720
so we don't get taken advantage of.

05:46.720 --> 05:48.320
You were right to stay alert.

05:48.950 --> 05:49.680
What about the others?

05:49.680 --> 05:51.740
Do you remember anything about them?

05:53.480 --> 05:55.409
It's okay. No rush. Take your time.

05:57.120 --> 05:59.720
I think there was one
with a scar on his face.

06:00.310 --> 06:02.390
I've seen him before

06:02.750 --> 06:04.680
at the long-distance bus station.

06:05.360 --> 06:06.270
Officer,

06:06.680 --> 06:08.030
even though it was raining yesterday,

06:08.030 --> 06:09.040
they made quite a commotion

06:09.040 --> 06:10.510
when they attacked.

06:10.880 --> 06:12.000
You could ask around the neighborhood.

06:12.000 --> 06:13.460
There might be witnesses.

06:13.920 --> 06:14.980
We'll look into it.

06:21.800 --> 06:22.730
Watch your step.

06:24.630 --> 06:25.160
Xiaolan.

06:27.390 --> 06:28.120
Sis Zhenzhu.

06:28.390 --> 06:29.250
I was reckless.

06:29.390 --> 06:30.920
I almost made things worse.

06:31.190 --> 06:33.120
I don't deserve to be your brother.

06:33.920 --> 06:34.430
San,

06:35.310 --> 06:37.440
you were just trying to stand up for me.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.240
This isn't on you.

06:40.360 --> 06:41.820
I didn't think it through.

06:46.430 --> 06:47.070
Well...

06:47.270 --> 06:49.000
Let's talk over food, shall we?

06:49.480 --> 06:50.360
I drove all night.

06:50.360 --> 06:51.159
I'm starving.

06:51.390 --> 06:51.790
Right.

06:52.159 --> 06:53.090
Let's eat first.

06:59.430 --> 07:00.830
Let me see.

07:02.160 --> 07:03.270
This one, one of these.

07:03.270 --> 07:03.720
Wei!

07:04.640 --> 07:05.040
Sis Bai.

07:05.040 --> 07:05.630
Here, here.

07:05.630 --> 07:06.270
Sit down.

07:06.680 --> 07:07.360
And...

07:07.510 --> 07:08.560
t-these two as well.

07:08.560 --> 07:10.160
Less oil, less salt,

07:10.190 --> 07:10.920
and no chili.

07:12.000 --> 07:12.600
Thank you.

07:17.360 --> 07:18.830
How about chrysanthemum tea for drinks?

07:18.830 --> 07:19.800
It can reduce internal heat.

07:19.800 --> 07:21.400
Chrysanthemum tea? Really?

07:21.410 --> 07:22.310
Just chrysanthemum tea, then.

07:22.310 --> 07:23.000
Chrysanthemum tea.

07:23.000 --> 07:23.390
Alright.

07:23.390 --> 07:25.070
You're teasing me too?

07:25.680 --> 07:27.270
I wouldn't dare.

07:27.270 --> 07:28.560
You scared the hell out of me.

07:28.560 --> 07:29.820
How are your injuries?

07:29.870 --> 07:30.870
I'm heading to the hospital this afternoon

07:30.870 --> 07:32.130
to visit You's mother.

07:32.140 --> 07:33.240
Why don't you come with me

07:33.240 --> 07:35.370
and have your injuries checked again?

07:37.159 --> 07:38.390
I'm fine.

07:38.390 --> 07:39.510
Just flesh wounds.

07:39.630 --> 07:40.800
No broken bones.

07:41.210 --> 07:42.360
Xiaolan told me everything.

07:42.360 --> 07:43.850
She specifically asked me
to order light food for you,

07:43.850 --> 07:45.250
so I got you plain congee.

07:46.630 --> 07:47.290
You guys...

07:47.870 --> 07:48.930
Don't be like this.

07:49.120 --> 07:50.850
You're making me embarrassed.

07:51.950 --> 07:52.920
Where are the two of them?

07:52.920 --> 07:55.120
Parking the car. They'll be right here.

08:01.040 --> 08:01.600
Thanks.

08:06.600 --> 08:09.100
[Majestic Mahjong]

08:17.800 --> 08:18.270
Boss.

08:23.720 --> 08:24.430
What is it?

08:24.830 --> 08:25.680
Why the panic?

08:26.390 --> 08:27.920
About Bai Zhenzhu yesterday...

08:27.920 --> 08:29.650
They reported it to the police.

08:34.480 --> 08:36.270
What does that have to do with me?

08:36.270 --> 08:38.200
After I left the restaurant yesterday,

08:38.200 --> 08:39.460
I went to a karaoke bar.

08:39.630 --> 08:40.720
After karaoke,

08:40.789 --> 08:41.990
I came straight here.

08:42.080 --> 08:43.390
The owners of the karaoke,
the restaurant,

08:43.390 --> 08:44.480
and even the street stalls

08:44.480 --> 08:45.480
can all back me up.

08:45.960 --> 08:47.120
So what if she reported it?

08:47.120 --> 08:48.980
What the hell does it matter to me?

08:50.750 --> 08:51.480
Let's go eat.

09:08.550 --> 09:09.550
Have some of this.

09:12.120 --> 09:12.750
Sis Bai.

09:13.230 --> 09:14.770
Eat. It's so light.

09:14.910 --> 09:15.440
Eat up.

09:17.480 --> 09:18.880
Xiaolan, you were right.

09:19.440 --> 09:21.770
I almost led everyone down the wrong path.

09:22.750 --> 09:24.410
I got too carried away lately.

09:26.790 --> 09:27.750
Sis Bai, San,

09:28.410 --> 09:28.950
you didn't

09:28.950 --> 09:30.610
do anything illegal, did you?

09:32.600 --> 09:33.400
No, we didn't.

09:34.120 --> 09:35.480
And we never bullied

09:35.600 --> 09:36.460
anyone either.

09:37.510 --> 09:38.200
But lately,

09:38.440 --> 09:39.770
I've been leading my men

09:40.030 --> 09:41.360
to go head-to-head with Ke Yixiong

09:41.360 --> 09:42.690
and steal his business.

09:43.390 --> 09:45.590
Thinking about it now, I deserved this.

09:45.600 --> 09:46.800
It was a wake-up call.

09:47.360 --> 09:48.160
Because of me,

09:48.400 --> 09:49.910
my fellow disciples have all gotten

09:49.910 --> 09:51.910
caught up in this thrill of rivalry.

09:52.200 --> 09:54.060
Now, I can still keep them in line.

09:54.840 --> 09:56.550
But what if

09:57.270 --> 09:58.150
one day I can't?

10:00.000 --> 10:02.600
I still need to
lead everyone on the right path,

10:02.960 --> 10:04.560
doing legitimate business.

10:05.870 --> 10:06.510
Sis Bai,

10:07.120 --> 10:09.080
everyone acts on impulse sometimes.

10:09.080 --> 10:09.910
The difference lies in

10:09.910 --> 10:11.200
whether you can calm down

10:11.200 --> 10:13.000
and truly deal with the problem.

10:13.080 --> 10:15.140
It's good that you've figured it out.

10:17.080 --> 10:17.940
Well, Xiaolan,

10:18.850 --> 10:19.980
you reminded me too.

10:20.440 --> 10:22.840
I didn't think things through this time.

10:23.030 --> 10:24.090
I acted on impulse.

10:27.790 --> 10:28.480
San,

10:28.910 --> 10:31.720
there's actually something about you
I really don't get.

10:31.720 --> 10:33.510
Sis Bai and Ke Yixiong are

10:33.510 --> 10:35.120
competing for turf and business—

10:35.120 --> 10:36.550
that's to help her fellow disciples

10:36.550 --> 10:37.390
make a living.

10:37.550 --> 10:38.240
Yes, yes.

10:38.320 --> 10:40.910
But you... have your own business,

10:40.910 --> 10:43.270
and you've got nothing to do
with Ke Yixiong.

10:43.270 --> 10:44.510
You doing all this...

10:45.790 --> 10:47.250
Why exactly did he do that?

10:47.870 --> 10:48.670
Yeah, well...

10:49.140 --> 10:49.690
Why?

10:49.720 --> 10:51.570
Yeah, why exactly?

10:51.600 --> 10:52.960
When I first heard

10:52.960 --> 10:54.100
that San went to Longcheng,

10:54.100 --> 10:55.340
I was puzzled.

10:55.480 --> 10:56.670
You see, San has weathered

10:56.670 --> 10:58.200
more storms than any of us.

10:58.390 --> 10:58.910
Logically,

10:58.910 --> 11:00.720
he should've been
more level-headed than us,

11:00.720 --> 11:02.240
right? So, why?

11:02.910 --> 11:03.630
Yes, it's so strange.

11:03.630 --> 11:04.910
Why did he do that? Why?

11:04.910 --> 11:05.970
Why did you do that?

11:06.000 --> 11:06.930
For Sis Zhenzhu!

11:14.630 --> 11:15.960
I won't hide it anymore.

11:17.550 --> 11:18.950
Sis Zhenzhu was bullied.

11:19.120 --> 11:20.850
I just couldn't let that slide.

11:21.480 --> 11:22.240
But last night,

11:22.240 --> 11:23.970
Zhou Cheng asked me something.

11:24.840 --> 11:26.080
If I got locked up

11:26.100 --> 11:26.730
over this,

11:27.600 --> 11:29.270
we wouldn't be able to
face each other afterward—

11:29.270 --> 11:30.730
how could I live with that?

11:31.480 --> 11:32.540
I thought about it,

11:33.390 --> 11:34.650
and I couldn't bear it.

11:37.510 --> 11:38.120
San,

11:38.480 --> 11:40.240
what do you mean by that?

11:41.550 --> 11:42.750
I couldn't bear the thought of...

11:42.750 --> 11:44.550
never seeing Sis Zhenzhu again.

11:49.960 --> 11:50.690
Sis Zhenzhu,

11:51.270 --> 11:51.870
I...

11:53.080 --> 11:53.600
I...

11:55.360 --> 11:56.120
I...

11:57.550 --> 11:58.120
I...

12:02.080 --> 12:03.200
I still want to spar with you
in the future—

12:03.200 --> 12:04.390
that move you taught me last time:

12:04.390 --> 12:05.520
the Bai Family Fist.

12:06.940 --> 12:09.370
San, are you serious?

12:09.560 --> 12:09.910
Come on,

12:09.910 --> 12:11.030
you can't be

12:11.030 --> 12:12.090
this dense, right?

12:16.240 --> 12:17.080
Sis Zhenzhu, I like you.

12:17.080 --> 12:18.480
I don't know how you feel.

12:38.360 --> 12:39.320
I like you too.

12:44.510 --> 12:45.750
That's great! That's great!

12:45.750 --> 12:46.870
After all this time,

12:46.870 --> 12:48.200
you two finally got it out

12:48.200 --> 12:48.860
in the open!

12:49.600 --> 12:51.000
You two were driving me crazy just now.

12:51.000 --> 12:52.730
I almost stepped in to help him!

12:53.080 --> 12:53.540
Come on.

12:53.960 --> 12:55.270
A toast to love!

12:55.600 --> 12:56.060
Come on!

12:57.150 --> 12:58.220
To love!

12:58.240 --> 12:59.270
To love!

13:11.390 --> 13:12.020
Nurse,

13:12.150 --> 13:13.150
please be gentle.

13:13.360 --> 13:13.960
Thank you.

13:15.000 --> 13:17.060
Changing the dressing doesn't hurt.

13:18.480 --> 13:19.360
Be careful for the next few days,

13:19.360 --> 13:20.510
and don't get the wounds wet.

13:20.510 --> 13:21.640
Keep taking the anti-inflammatory meds.

13:21.640 --> 13:22.390
If you develop a fever

13:22.390 --> 13:23.150
or any other problems,

13:23.150 --> 13:24.960
come back to the hospital immediately.

13:24.960 --> 13:25.550
Nurse,

13:25.720 --> 13:26.270
is there anything else

13:26.270 --> 13:27.440
we need to watch out for?

13:27.440 --> 13:29.670
Please t-tell me everything.
I'll remember it all.

13:29.670 --> 13:30.210
You

13:30.240 --> 13:31.550
should make sure to protect her.

13:31.550 --> 13:32.320
How did this happen?

13:32.320 --> 13:33.600
She's black and blue all over.

13:33.600 --> 13:34.440
Yes, yes.

13:35.440 --> 13:37.300
I really didn't protect her well.

13:37.750 --> 13:39.410
Nurse Sun, come here a moment.

13:39.510 --> 13:39.970
Coming.

13:40.620 --> 13:41.170
All done.

13:41.200 --> 13:42.910
Rest up, and then you're free to go.

13:42.910 --> 13:43.670
Thank you.

13:50.510 --> 13:52.110
Careful, don't catch a cold.

14:07.000 --> 14:07.730
Sis Zhenzhu.

14:09.510 --> 14:10.440
I'm a rough man.

14:11.320 --> 14:13.000
I'm not good with sweet talk.

14:13.870 --> 14:16.720
And I'm not as good at business
or making money as you.

14:16.720 --> 14:18.000
What I said earlier about protecting you—

14:18.000 --> 14:18.790
that was me talking big.

14:18.730 --> 14:23.230
♪ I'm never tired by your side
during this long journey ♪

14:19.240 --> 14:20.570
But I'll work hard at it!

14:23.710 --> 14:28.910
♪ We walk through
every leg of it together ♪

14:25.200 --> 14:25.750
San.

14:26.910 --> 14:28.120
Actually, I don't need

14:28.120 --> 14:29.320
anyone to protect me.

14:29.440 --> 14:31.510
♪ As I climb over a peak ♪

14:29.960 --> 14:31.120
What I want

14:31.480 --> 14:33.550
is someone I can talk to

14:31.530 --> 14:34.110
♪ Another peak appears before my eyes ♪

14:33.960 --> 14:35.150
in everyday life...

14:34.600 --> 14:36.130
♪ Keep the goals high ♪

14:36.150 --> 14:39.360
♪ Let your ideals always lead the way ♪

14:37.360 --> 14:38.320
and a partner who can fight by my side

14:38.320 --> 14:39.910
when danger comes.

14:40.120 --> 14:42.050
♪ The road ahead is rough and steep ♪

14:40.550 --> 14:41.480
You already are.

14:42.070 --> 14:44.720
♪ Yet we keep going ♪

14:44.970 --> 14:50.170
♪ May we embrace
both sorrow and joy in this life ♪

14:50.900 --> 14:52.830
♪ Moments of joy and sorrow ♪

14:52.240 --> 14:52.750
Sis...

14:52.860 --> 14:55.680
♪ Swirl around us ♪

14:53.510 --> 14:54.640
Why is your face red?

14:54.960 --> 14:56.720
Ouch, ouch...

14:55.950 --> 14:57.050
♪ In the wind ♪

14:59.160 --> 15:00.130
Sorry, sis.

15:05.840 --> 15:07.440
Don't call me "Sis" anymore.

15:08.360 --> 15:09.290
Call me Zhenzhu.

15:14.840 --> 15:15.370
Zhenzhu.

15:17.150 --> 15:17.630
San.

15:20.910 --> 15:21.440
Zhenzhu!

15:26.030 --> 15:26.480
Li,

15:26.750 --> 15:27.390
take a break.

15:27.390 --> 15:28.250
Come eat first.

15:28.320 --> 15:29.670
I ordered all these for you.

15:29.670 --> 15:30.730
There are too many.

15:30.870 --> 15:32.360
Two buns are enough for me.

15:32.880 --> 15:33.970
That won't do.

15:34.000 --> 15:34.860
Give that to me.

15:35.200 --> 15:36.000
Let me tell you,

15:36.000 --> 15:37.510
you work so hard
to take care of your mom every day.

15:37.510 --> 15:39.040
You need proper nutrition.

15:39.360 --> 15:41.030
Vegetables, meat, eggs—

15:41.200 --> 15:42.200
you need them all.

15:42.330 --> 15:43.450
Only by eating well

15:43.480 --> 15:45.360
will you have the strength
to take better care of your mom.

15:45.360 --> 15:45.840
Eat up.

15:49.840 --> 15:50.720
Come and eat too.

15:50.720 --> 15:51.520
Stop working.

15:51.750 --> 15:52.680
Coming, coming.

15:59.440 --> 16:00.040
Is it good?

16:00.490 --> 16:01.420
It's delicious!

16:03.580 --> 16:04.600
I still want to hire a caregiver

16:04.600 --> 16:05.390
for my mom.

16:05.750 --> 16:06.630
Things at the Golden Sands Pool project

16:06.630 --> 16:07.760
are getting busier.

16:07.840 --> 16:08.480
Even Ms. Xia

16:08.480 --> 16:09.840
has to work overtime often.

16:09.840 --> 16:10.960
As her assistant,

16:11.030 --> 16:12.210
leaving on time every day

16:12.210 --> 16:13.740
doesn't feel appropriate.

16:14.390 --> 16:16.070
Xiaolan won't mind.

16:17.840 --> 16:18.900
Here's some water.

16:19.320 --> 16:20.790
Ms. Xia hired an assistant

16:21.340 --> 16:22.670
precisely because she's too busy.

16:22.670 --> 16:23.930
She's kind not to mind,

16:24.330 --> 16:25.080
but I can't be

16:25.080 --> 16:26.140
oblivious to that.

16:26.670 --> 16:28.470
Plus, with my family situation,

16:28.480 --> 16:29.390
she still hired me

16:29.390 --> 16:30.790
and lent me money for my mom's treatment.

16:30.790 --> 16:32.390
I need to repay her kindness.

16:32.510 --> 16:33.120
Besides,

16:33.480 --> 16:34.840
I want to take on more work,

16:34.840 --> 16:36.240
get a promotion and a raise soon,

16:36.240 --> 16:36.910
and pay back

16:37.030 --> 16:38.830
the money I owe the company ASAP.

16:39.000 --> 16:39.630
And then?

16:41.360 --> 16:42.150
Then what?

16:42.870 --> 16:44.200
Y-You're still so young

16:44.200 --> 16:45.060
and so capable.

16:45.220 --> 16:46.720
You'll definitely make it big

16:46.720 --> 16:47.630
and earn big money.

16:47.630 --> 16:48.570
Once you do,

16:48.670 --> 16:49.630
is there anything

16:49.630 --> 16:50.690
you dream of doing?

16:51.510 --> 16:53.310
Make it big and earn big money...

16:53.630 --> 16:54.320
I don't dare think

16:54.320 --> 16:55.240
that far ahead.

16:57.120 --> 16:57.910
I just hope

16:58.270 --> 16:59.000
I can give my mom

16:59.000 --> 17:00.030
a good life.

17:00.960 --> 17:01.840
When she wakes up,

17:01.840 --> 17:03.700
I'll take her around Shengcheng.

17:03.910 --> 17:04.920
She hasn't really had a chance

17:04.920 --> 17:06.349
to see the place properly.

17:06.349 --> 17:07.589
If there's a chance,

17:07.920 --> 17:09.319
I want to take her to Hushi

17:09.440 --> 17:10.300
and Jingcheng.

17:12.829 --> 17:13.440
Kang Wei,

17:13.880 --> 17:14.680
what's wrong?

17:17.200 --> 17:18.310
Uh, nothing.

17:19.069 --> 17:20.030
I just think

17:20.400 --> 17:22.270
you look really pretty when you smile.

17:22.270 --> 17:23.790
You should smile more often.

17:23.790 --> 17:25.400
A smile always lifts your spirits.

17:25.400 --> 17:26.240
And when you're in good spirits,

17:26.240 --> 17:27.440
life gets better too.

17:28.069 --> 17:29.480
What you said is really nice too.

17:29.480 --> 17:30.480
You and your mom

17:30.750 --> 17:32.610
will definitely have a good life.

17:33.640 --> 17:34.400
Hurry up and eat.

17:34.400 --> 17:35.600
Let's eat. Let's eat.

17:36.550 --> 17:37.750
Here, have some meat.

17:39.440 --> 17:40.070
I'll help myself.

17:40.070 --> 17:41.130
Okay, okay, you eat it yourself.

17:41.130 --> 17:42.950
[Marriage Registration Office
of Shengcheng Civil Affairs Bureau]

17:47.200 --> 17:48.800
Congratulations to you two.

18:01.000 --> 18:01.460
Come on.

18:01.720 --> 18:02.480
First of all,

18:03.000 --> 18:04.290
I want to thank everyone

18:04.290 --> 18:04.970
for

18:05.030 --> 18:07.230
all the help and support you've given me

18:07.240 --> 18:08.370
and Comrade Liu Fen.

18:08.510 --> 18:10.030
And today, you've taken time

18:10.030 --> 18:11.490
out of your busy schedules

18:11.790 --> 18:13.450
to come and celebrate with us.

18:13.510 --> 18:14.570
From today onward,

18:14.960 --> 18:16.110
we're a couple—

18:16.720 --> 18:17.720
husband and wife—

18:17.750 --> 18:19.150
officially and legally.

18:20.400 --> 18:21.030
Thank you, everyone!

18:21.030 --> 18:21.790
I'll down this glass.

18:21.790 --> 18:22.720
-Great!
-Great!

18:27.480 --> 18:28.200
He really drank it all!

18:28.200 --> 18:29.550
We haven't clicked yet.

18:30.070 --> 18:31.030
From now on,

18:31.400 --> 18:32.690
my wife calls the shots.

18:32.690 --> 18:33.400
-See?
-Honey.

18:33.400 --> 18:34.260
Learn from him.

18:34.750 --> 18:35.160
Honey,

18:35.350 --> 18:36.720
do you want to say a few words?

18:36.720 --> 18:37.590
Me?

18:39.000 --> 18:39.400
Okay.

18:39.680 --> 18:40.240
I'll say a few words.

18:40.240 --> 18:40.640
Great.

18:41.510 --> 18:43.350
We're all family here,

18:43.680 --> 18:45.880
so I'm not afraid of
saying something wrong.

18:45.880 --> 18:47.070
Actually, I have

18:47.920 --> 18:49.400
so many things to say,

18:49.720 --> 18:50.400
but

18:50.680 --> 18:52.210
I don't know where to start.

18:53.510 --> 18:55.570
Many years ago, if someone had told me

18:55.590 --> 18:58.590
that I could leave
that little village in Yunan

18:58.920 --> 19:00.520
and come live in Shengcheng,

19:01.070 --> 19:02.130
that I could become

19:02.440 --> 19:04.240
the manager of a clothing store,

19:05.160 --> 19:06.160
and marry someone

19:06.310 --> 19:07.960
as wonderful as Tang,

19:08.880 --> 19:10.440
I wouldn't have dared to dream it—

19:10.440 --> 19:12.240
it would've seemed like a fantasy!

19:12.240 --> 19:13.550
But as time went on,

19:14.160 --> 19:15.000
day by day,

19:16.030 --> 19:17.760
all of that actually came true.

19:18.110 --> 19:18.680
Fen,

19:18.960 --> 19:20.310
that's not strange at all.

19:20.310 --> 19:21.750
You earned all of this through hard work—

19:21.750 --> 19:22.610
you deserve it!

19:23.880 --> 19:24.550
I just feel

19:24.550 --> 19:25.750
that I'm so lucky.

19:26.110 --> 19:27.440
I'm truly so fortunate.

19:28.400 --> 19:29.530
But I know in my heart

19:29.880 --> 19:32.200
that I owe all of this

19:32.550 --> 19:34.640
to my family here

19:34.880 --> 19:36.350
and friends.

19:36.880 --> 19:38.640
It's you who have been helping me,

19:38.640 --> 19:39.970
helping Xiaolan and me.

19:41.440 --> 19:42.640
First, I want to thank

19:43.310 --> 19:45.040
my brother and sister-in-law.

19:45.310 --> 19:46.720
If you hadn't

19:46.720 --> 19:48.440
taken Xiaolan and me in back then,

19:48.440 --> 19:50.440
we wouldn't have been able to get by.

19:51.550 --> 19:52.200
Thank you.

19:53.110 --> 19:53.480
Fen,

19:53.720 --> 19:54.580
don't say that.

19:54.880 --> 19:57.010
We're family. It goes without saying.

19:59.270 --> 20:01.110
I also want to thank Mr. Chen

20:01.640 --> 20:02.900
for trusting me so much

20:03.070 --> 20:04.720
and putting me in charge of

20:04.720 --> 20:05.580
Luna's stores.

20:05.590 --> 20:06.190
Thank you.

20:06.240 --> 20:06.840
No, no, no.

20:07.240 --> 20:08.120
You're being too formal.

20:08.120 --> 20:09.440
I've always believed work and friendship

20:09.440 --> 20:10.480
are separate things.

20:10.480 --> 20:11.540
You do your job well

20:11.590 --> 20:12.990
because you're capable.

20:13.590 --> 20:14.190
Thank you.

20:20.550 --> 20:21.610
I also want to thank

20:22.270 --> 20:23.070
Granny Yu!

20:24.640 --> 20:26.590
We aren't related by blood.

20:27.160 --> 20:28.270
I lost my parents

20:28.830 --> 20:29.790
at a young age,

20:30.680 --> 20:32.510
so it was just my brother and me,

20:32.960 --> 20:34.360
depending on each other.

20:35.030 --> 20:36.200
After meeting you,

20:37.310 --> 20:38.880
you've always cared for me

20:38.880 --> 20:40.010
with all your heart.

20:40.680 --> 20:43.680
You always worried
I'd be taken advantage of

20:44.200 --> 20:44.880
or suffer.

20:45.750 --> 20:47.610
And you've always encouraged me.

20:48.030 --> 20:48.720
Actually,

20:49.270 --> 20:50.110
in my heart,

20:51.030 --> 20:52.750
you've long been my family.

20:57.160 --> 20:57.640
I...

20:59.550 --> 21:00.400
Well,

21:01.480 --> 21:04.070
t-that's all because your steamed buns

21:04.640 --> 21:05.590
are delicious.

21:12.590 --> 21:14.110
And my daughter, Xiaolan.

21:15.160 --> 21:16.760
I haven't been a good mother.

21:17.510 --> 21:18.830
I have no great talents

21:19.640 --> 21:21.840
and haven't been able to do much for you.

21:22.000 --> 21:22.920
In the past,

21:23.440 --> 21:24.970
I caused you a lot of trouble

21:25.110 --> 21:26.350
and made you suffer.

21:28.350 --> 21:30.240
You're the one who kept pulling me forward

21:30.240 --> 21:31.370
to get us here today.

21:32.470 --> 21:33.310
My Xiaolan

21:34.070 --> 21:35.270
is the best daughter

21:35.830 --> 21:36.830
in the world.

21:38.920 --> 21:39.590
Mom,

21:40.160 --> 21:41.030
don't say that.

21:41.720 --> 21:42.440
Today isn't the time

21:42.440 --> 21:43.970
to dwell on past hardships.

21:44.750 --> 21:46.640
It's time to look forward to the future.

21:46.640 --> 21:47.750
I wish you and Uncle Tang

21:47.750 --> 21:49.010
an even better future!

21:50.310 --> 21:50.910
Thank you.

21:55.960 --> 21:56.490
Finally,

21:57.790 --> 21:59.050
I want to thank my Tang.

21:59.440 --> 22:00.750
You want to thank me too?

22:00.750 --> 22:01.810
Then, pour me some.

22:03.680 --> 22:05.480
Thank you for treating me so well

22:05.720 --> 22:07.960
and for waiting for me to grow.

22:08.680 --> 22:10.880
It was also you who made me realize that I

22:11.200 --> 22:12.160
deserve to be loved

22:12.160 --> 22:13.240
and to be happy.

22:14.790 --> 22:15.830
As for the rest...

22:17.240 --> 22:18.700
No need for all the thanks.

22:19.400 --> 22:20.860
If there's anything more,

22:21.070 --> 22:21.590
Fen,

22:21.880 --> 22:23.410
let's talk about it at home.

22:24.160 --> 22:25.030
Come on!

22:25.310 --> 22:26.270
Come on!

22:26.480 --> 22:28.520
We also need to thank the big boss

22:28.550 --> 22:29.310
and the big star here

22:29.310 --> 22:30.160
for coming to join

22:30.160 --> 22:31.360
our gathering today!

22:31.640 --> 22:31.960
We're so honored!

22:31.960 --> 22:32.640
Yong,

22:32.640 --> 22:34.040
you're being too polite.

22:34.240 --> 22:35.270
Here in Shengcheng,

22:35.270 --> 22:36.310
we're all one family.

22:36.310 --> 22:37.000
That's right.

22:37.000 --> 22:37.550
We're one family!

22:37.550 --> 22:38.310
We're family.

22:38.310 --> 22:39.310
Thank you, everyone!

22:39.310 --> 22:39.550
Cheers!

22:39.550 --> 22:40.630
Wishing you a happy marriage!

22:40.630 --> 22:42.680
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations.

22:42.680 --> 22:44.000
And most importantly,

22:44.550 --> 22:46.170
Fen was married off

22:46.190 --> 22:47.100
from my home.

22:47.920 --> 22:48.510
Xiaolan,

22:49.480 --> 22:50.310
from now on,

22:50.360 --> 22:51.960
this is your natal home, too.

22:52.440 --> 22:52.840
Great.

22:55.110 --> 22:55.570
Cheers.

22:55.880 --> 22:56.590
To another home.

22:56.590 --> 22:57.480
-Cheers.
-Great!

22:57.480 --> 22:59.280
-Thank you, everyone!
-Cheers!

23:17.110 --> 23:17.970
Mom, it's fine.

23:18.310 --> 23:19.440
It's not far anyway.

23:19.830 --> 23:20.890
Come back anytime.

23:22.880 --> 23:23.810
When I have time,

23:24.240 --> 23:26.640
I'll come back
and cook you something nice.

23:28.070 --> 23:28.600
Let's go.

23:28.830 --> 23:30.290
I'll walk you downstairs.

23:43.070 --> 23:43.960
Okay, let's put it in together.

23:43.960 --> 23:44.310
Okay.

23:45.350 --> 23:46.270
It's a bit heavy.

23:46.270 --> 23:47.330
Easy. Put it there.

23:51.270 --> 23:52.530
Take care of yourself.

23:53.110 --> 23:54.040
Come back often.

23:56.250 --> 23:56.790
Goodbye, Auntie.

23:56.790 --> 23:57.650
We're off then.

23:58.110 --> 23:58.750
Bye, Mom.

23:58.960 --> 24:00.290
Let's go. Get in the car.

24:22.010 --> 24:23.070
What are you dawdling around for?

24:23.070 --> 24:24.160
What are you looking at?

24:24.160 --> 24:25.290
Hurry up and load it!

24:25.920 --> 24:27.590
They're waiting for
the delivery over there!

24:27.590 --> 24:28.310
My wife.

24:28.590 --> 24:30.250
What do you mean, "your wife"?

24:30.450 --> 24:31.200
Even if it were your mother,

24:31.200 --> 24:33.240
you still have to stack the goods for me!
Hurry up!

24:33.240 --> 24:35.170
We need to get these delivered now!

24:48.830 --> 24:49.480
Xia Dajun,

24:50.210 --> 24:51.550
if you keep dawdling like this,

24:51.550 --> 24:53.450
I'll find someone else
to make the delivery!

24:53.450 --> 24:54.510
Can you do it or not?

25:00.070 --> 25:01.160
Let's have some herbal tea.

25:01.160 --> 25:01.510
Okay.

25:03.200 --> 25:03.600
Ma'am,

25:03.880 --> 25:05.210
two cups of 24 Herbs tea.

25:05.210 --> 25:06.140
Coming right up.

25:10.880 --> 25:12.340
Here are your herbal teas.

25:12.640 --> 25:13.970
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

25:18.510 --> 25:19.590
I didn't expect

25:20.070 --> 25:20.880
my mom to get married

25:20.880 --> 25:21.680
before me.

25:23.960 --> 25:24.760
What's wrong?

25:25.510 --> 25:26.910
Feeling a bit emotional?

25:27.590 --> 25:28.510
Or...

25:29.240 --> 25:30.840
are you missing your own mom?

25:33.070 --> 25:33.730
Zhou Cheng,

25:34.920 --> 25:36.110
actually, I rarely

25:36.110 --> 25:37.370
think of them anymore.

25:38.070 --> 25:39.000
Sometimes,

25:39.590 --> 25:41.310
I've completely come to see Liu Fen

25:41.310 --> 25:42.550
as my own mom.

25:43.960 --> 25:45.830
All that childhood longing for a mother

25:45.830 --> 25:47.030
that had nowhere to go

25:47.110 --> 25:48.840
finally has somewhere to land.

25:51.350 --> 25:53.160
That must be a blessing for

25:53.960 --> 25:55.290
both you and Auntie Liu.

25:57.200 --> 25:58.070
But...

25:58.510 --> 25:59.440
sometimes,

26:00.550 --> 26:01.950
I still secretly wonder.

26:02.400 --> 26:03.350
I wonder...

26:05.350 --> 26:06.880
if my own mom and dad

26:07.350 --> 26:07.960
saw you,

26:08.400 --> 26:10.060
what would their reaction be?

26:10.960 --> 26:12.420
Would they be like Liu Fen,

26:12.530 --> 26:13.400
seeing her son-in-law

26:13.400 --> 26:14.730
as perfect in every way?

26:15.160 --> 26:16.290
Or would they be like

26:16.350 --> 26:17.920
my uncle and Uncle Tang,

26:18.350 --> 26:19.310
feeling like their precious daughter

26:19.310 --> 26:20.640
got "snatched by a pig"?

26:23.070 --> 26:23.510
Well,

26:24.120 --> 26:24.980
now I'm the pig.

26:25.960 --> 26:26.680
I'll take it.

26:26.680 --> 26:27.750
Still better than

26:27.920 --> 26:30.320
being compared to
cow dung next to a flower.

26:33.960 --> 26:34.490
Xiaolan.

26:35.880 --> 26:36.830
I think

26:37.590 --> 26:38.720
your mom and dad

26:40.000 --> 26:41.530
might have already seen us.

26:42.830 --> 26:43.270
Look.

26:44.350 --> 26:45.350
The world

26:45.960 --> 26:47.490
is such a mysterious place.

26:47.750 --> 26:48.310
Maybe

26:48.310 --> 26:49.790
in some other dimension,

26:50.440 --> 26:52.370
they've already seen everything.

26:55.440 --> 26:56.270
Mom, Dad,

26:57.200 --> 26:58.480
if you can see me,

26:59.720 --> 27:00.970
you must be happy with

27:01.000 --> 27:02.530
who I've become now, right?

27:17.590 --> 27:18.450
So, do you think

27:18.550 --> 27:20.550
this part needs to be revised again?

27:21.000 --> 27:22.200
I think we still need to upgrade

27:22.200 --> 27:22.800
this part.

27:22.920 --> 27:23.590
This part?

27:23.880 --> 27:24.480
Okay. I'll...

27:24.480 --> 27:25.640
Ms. Xia, are you having a date

27:25.640 --> 27:26.440
in the office?

27:27.310 --> 27:28.310
Watch your image.

27:28.400 --> 27:29.440
I'm consulting Mr. Zhou

27:29.440 --> 27:30.510
on a legal matter.

27:30.750 --> 27:32.010
Do you need something?

27:33.030 --> 27:33.790
I'm just worried you might be

27:33.790 --> 27:35.450
neglecting work, that's all.

27:36.240 --> 27:36.640
Here.

27:36.880 --> 27:38.070
This is the marketing plan

27:38.070 --> 27:38.920
for Electronics City.

27:38.920 --> 27:39.880
I've reviewed it.

27:39.880 --> 27:41.270
There are no legal risks.

27:41.270 --> 27:41.750
Mr. Du, you can

27:41.750 --> 27:43.010
proceed with the plan.

27:43.920 --> 27:44.750
Ms. Xia...

27:45.680 --> 27:47.610
aren't you going to help me with it?

27:48.110 --> 27:48.920
Du Zhaohui,

27:49.430 --> 27:50.790
you paid the consultation fee,

27:50.790 --> 27:51.550
and I gave you the idea

27:51.550 --> 27:52.750
of Electronics City.

27:52.790 --> 27:54.550
That was already more than sufficient.

27:54.550 --> 27:55.660
This marketing plan

27:55.660 --> 27:56.860
is already a bonus.

27:57.070 --> 27:58.200
If you want anything else,

27:58.200 --> 27:59.660
I'll have to charge extra.

28:00.680 --> 28:01.400
Even if you wanted to charge me now,

28:01.400 --> 28:02.260
I couldn't pay.

28:03.160 --> 28:04.410
Let me give you an update—

28:04.410 --> 28:05.440
the interior build-out of

28:05.440 --> 28:07.000
Electronics City is almost done.

28:07.000 --> 28:08.130
We can open anytime.

28:08.310 --> 28:09.070
What do you think—

28:09.070 --> 28:10.030
should we pick an auspicious day

28:10.030 --> 28:10.790
to open now?

28:12.440 --> 28:14.640
Your father is going to
announce the results

28:14.640 --> 28:16.040
at his birthday banquet.

28:16.400 --> 28:18.860
Let's make it three days
before the banquet.

28:18.880 --> 28:19.550
Three days?

28:20.160 --> 28:21.750
How much can we make in just three days?

28:21.750 --> 28:23.160
And 30 days—so what?

28:23.750 --> 28:24.480
Trust me.

28:24.750 --> 28:25.440
Your father

28:25.440 --> 28:27.110
won't just look at the immediate figures.

28:27.110 --> 28:27.960
He will also look at

28:27.960 --> 28:29.290
future profitability.

28:30.270 --> 28:30.830
Fine.

28:31.030 --> 28:33.350
I'll trust your judgment, Ms. Xia.

28:35.310 --> 28:36.040
Well then...

28:36.940 --> 28:37.870
I'm heading out.

28:38.780 --> 28:40.180
Do you want to walk me out?

28:47.240 --> 28:47.840
Oh, right.

28:48.440 --> 28:51.030
There's been progress
on the smuggling case lately.

28:51.030 --> 28:53.270
I might've... misunderstood Du Zhaohui.

28:53.270 --> 28:54.160
He really hasn't been involved

28:54.160 --> 28:55.750
in his family's business for a long time.

28:55.750 --> 28:57.350
Do you remember that he once said

28:57.350 --> 28:59.000
Xia Dajun saved his life?

28:59.640 --> 29:01.190
At that time, someone really did

29:01.190 --> 29:02.650
try to take revenge on him.

29:02.920 --> 29:03.720
The Du family,

29:03.920 --> 29:05.400
for the sake of smuggling profits,

29:05.400 --> 29:07.330
wouldn't even spare their own son.

29:07.510 --> 29:09.030
That's not necessarily true.

29:09.030 --> 29:10.880
The people weren't sent by Du Chengrong.

29:10.880 --> 29:12.410
Du Chengrong has two wives,

29:12.510 --> 29:13.840
countless mistresses,

29:13.960 --> 29:15.560
and illegitimate children.

29:17.240 --> 29:18.200
The Du family

29:18.640 --> 29:20.030
might be far messier

29:20.310 --> 29:21.240
than it appears.

29:22.750 --> 29:24.160
Born into such a family,

29:25.120 --> 29:26.320
no wonder Du Zhaohui

29:26.350 --> 29:27.750
never plays by the rules.

29:35.790 --> 29:37.920
I still get butterflies when I see her.

29:41.350 --> 29:42.680
Go straight to the port.

29:42.880 --> 29:44.070
Let's go back to Gangdao.

29:44.070 --> 29:44.640
Young Master,

29:44.640 --> 29:46.900
you had a golf appointment with Mr. Tang.

29:47.440 --> 29:48.440
What golf?

29:49.510 --> 29:50.110
Xia Xiaolan has come up with

29:50.110 --> 29:51.310
so many clever ideas.

29:52.070 --> 29:54.200
Someone has to help her make them happen.

29:54.200 --> 29:56.030
Otherwise, my money would be wasted.

29:56.030 --> 29:56.790
If I remember correctly,

29:56.790 --> 29:57.830
Young Master, that check

29:57.830 --> 29:59.270
seems to be a dud.

29:59.850 --> 30:01.760
Do I need you to remind me? Just drive.

30:01.760 --> 30:03.490
I was only trying to be helpful.

30:07.320 --> 30:11.390
[Gangdao]

30:13.480 --> 30:15.000
Young Master! Young Master!

30:15.000 --> 30:15.650
I found it.

30:15.680 --> 30:16.480
Mr. Chen's company

30:16.480 --> 30:17.940
is right in this building.

30:18.880 --> 30:20.040
After all these years,

30:20.040 --> 30:20.770
Chen is still

30:20.790 --> 30:22.200
stuck in this dump.

30:22.270 --> 30:23.640
How's he supposed to do big business here?

30:23.640 --> 30:24.480
Drive. Let's go.

30:24.480 --> 30:24.810
Okay.

30:29.160 --> 30:30.200
Second Young Master!

30:30.200 --> 30:30.960
Du Zhaoji!

30:47.960 --> 30:48.790
Weird.

30:49.030 --> 30:50.230
Why is Du Zhaoji here?

30:51.030 --> 30:51.830
He didn't look this way, did he?

30:51.830 --> 30:52.760
No, no, no.

30:52.790 --> 30:53.240
Relax.

30:53.480 --> 30:54.920
The Second Young Master looks

30:54.920 --> 30:57.270
even more afraid of
running into acquaintances than you do.

30:57.270 --> 30:59.400
But he studied abroad from a young age.

31:00.010 --> 31:00.680
How could he have

31:00.680 --> 31:02.680
friends living in a place like this?

31:20.080 --> 31:21.480
Ms. Xia, here is the room key.

31:21.480 --> 31:22.610
Please keep it safe.

31:22.880 --> 31:24.640
The room is on the third floor.
This is the room number.

31:24.640 --> 31:25.970
Stay here for a few days.

31:26.200 --> 31:28.130
Someone will come looking for you.

31:39.240 --> 31:40.040
Sorry. Sorry.

31:40.350 --> 31:41.400
I didn't mean to.

31:41.550 --> 31:43.110
P-Please spare me.

31:47.760 --> 31:48.690
Raise your head.

31:58.240 --> 31:58.920
So tacky.

32:00.590 --> 32:01.680
Give me a way out!

32:01.960 --> 32:03.030
I'll do anything!

32:12.270 --> 32:14.530
Could it be that my plan actually worked?

32:16.110 --> 32:17.960
Du Zhaohui, oh, Du Zhaohui,

32:18.270 --> 32:19.640
you really are a genius.

32:20.750 --> 32:21.280
Let's go.

32:22.780 --> 32:24.880
As for the interior design of the theater,

32:24.880 --> 32:26.200
I want the audience

32:26.200 --> 32:28.260
to have a more immersive experience.

32:28.510 --> 32:29.030
So,

32:29.920 --> 32:31.510
I want to use the concept of a starry sky

32:31.510 --> 32:33.310
as the theme for this design.

32:33.590 --> 32:35.550
-When the lights go out...
-Ms. Xia.

32:35.550 --> 32:36.790
There's a call for you.

32:36.790 --> 32:37.960
When I'm studying with Mr. Mao,

32:37.960 --> 32:38.950
I don't take calls.

32:38.950 --> 32:40.590
It's from Ms. Ye.

32:40.960 --> 32:42.610
She said she's
returning to Gangdao tonight

32:42.610 --> 32:44.740
and wants to see you before she leaves.

32:45.480 --> 32:46.270
Ms. Ye?

32:53.070 --> 32:54.000
I thought

32:54.350 --> 32:55.680
we wouldn't meet again.

32:58.350 --> 32:59.830
I was rather rude last time.

32:59.830 --> 33:01.230
I hope you can forgive me.

33:02.830 --> 33:04.160
Here, give me your bowl.

33:05.310 --> 33:07.160
I know you're from Esheng.

33:07.720 --> 33:09.240
The last time I went to Jiangcheng
for a meeting,

33:09.240 --> 33:10.900
I really liked the food there.

33:11.120 --> 33:11.680
I'm not sure

33:11.680 --> 33:13.240
how authentic this restaurant is,

33:13.240 --> 33:15.030
but I heard the lotus root soup is good.

33:15.030 --> 33:15.560
Try some.

33:16.400 --> 33:16.750
Here.

33:24.880 --> 33:25.590
You're still the same as

33:25.590 --> 33:26.860
when I first met you—

33:26.920 --> 33:28.580
always putting others first.

33:32.430 --> 33:33.200
So...

33:33.830 --> 33:36.090
why did you come to Shengcheng this time?

33:39.600 --> 33:40.760
There was so much

33:40.790 --> 33:42.390
I didn't get to say last time.

33:42.720 --> 33:43.920
But after I went back,

33:44.310 --> 33:45.400
I thought a lot.

33:46.880 --> 33:48.080
If it weren't for you,

33:48.270 --> 33:49.930
I wouldn't be where I am today.

33:50.070 --> 33:51.530
So I invited you here today

33:51.830 --> 33:52.790
to tell you that

33:53.480 --> 33:55.280
even though Du Zhaoji is my boss,

33:55.830 --> 33:56.830
regarding

33:56.830 --> 33:57.690
your kindness,

33:58.070 --> 33:59.000
I, Ye Xiaoqiong,

33:59.240 --> 33:59.970
will repay it

34:00.480 --> 34:01.590
many times over!

34:04.960 --> 34:05.560
Let's eat.

34:07.110 --> 34:08.000
Ye Xiaoqiong

34:08.000 --> 34:09.590
came all the way to Shengcheng to see you.

34:09.590 --> 34:11.280
Isn't she afraid her boss, Du Zhaoji,

34:11.280 --> 34:12.440
will get suspicious?

34:12.440 --> 34:14.320
The fact that she came to
see me so openly

34:14.320 --> 34:15.100
shows

34:15.120 --> 34:16.960
Du Zhaoji has complete confidence

34:16.960 --> 34:18.150
in Ye Xiaoqiong's loyalty.

34:18.150 --> 34:19.280
But that confidence

34:19.280 --> 34:21.280
definitely isn't born of friendship.

34:21.280 --> 34:22.540
It's because Du Zhaoji

34:22.590 --> 34:24.400
has something on Ye Xiaoqiong.

34:24.880 --> 34:26.510
I'm guessing Ye Xiaoqiong's revenge

34:26.510 --> 34:27.230
relied on

34:27.230 --> 34:28.290
Du Zhaoji's power.

34:29.800 --> 34:31.330
Ye Xiaoqiong really jumped

34:31.520 --> 34:33.650
out of the frying pan and into the fire.

34:34.449 --> 34:35.370
Ye Xiaoqiong

34:35.400 --> 34:36.710
is no longer the pushover

34:36.710 --> 34:38.110
we met back then.

34:38.710 --> 34:40.150
The fact that she's managed to
secure a place

34:40.150 --> 34:40.900
by Du Zhaoji's side

34:40.900 --> 34:42.400
shows she's extraordinary.

34:42.400 --> 34:43.460
But no matter what,

34:43.840 --> 34:45.030
I still hope she can

34:45.030 --> 34:46.090
get what she wants.

34:47.710 --> 34:48.480
No one in the Du family

34:48.480 --> 34:49.610
is easy to deal with.

34:50.070 --> 34:50.960
All that can be found

34:50.960 --> 34:52.150
about Du Zhaoji is

34:52.170 --> 34:54.690
that he studied abroad
since middle school.

34:55.190 --> 34:56.190
After returning,

34:56.190 --> 34:57.960
he's been working for the family business.

34:57.960 --> 34:59.280
His style

34:59.280 --> 35:00.280
is indeed very much like

35:00.280 --> 35:02.000
that of a traditional business elite.

35:02.000 --> 35:03.000
He's also well regarded

35:03.000 --> 35:04.200
by the outside world.

35:04.400 --> 35:06.110
In this competition with Du Zhaohui,

35:06.110 --> 35:07.320
he's chosen the manufacturing sector.

35:07.320 --> 35:08.030
He even acquired a production line

35:08.030 --> 35:09.480
in Southeast Asia.

35:10.000 --> 35:11.930
He really has a knack for business.

35:13.150 --> 35:16.070
However, compared to the concept
of Electronics City,

35:16.070 --> 35:18.670
he still lacks
a bit of foresight and boldness.

35:19.480 --> 35:19.880
Well,

35:20.070 --> 35:21.000
of course.

35:21.420 --> 35:22.360
Electronics City

35:22.360 --> 35:23.910
has you as its strategist

35:24.280 --> 35:25.800
from the future.

35:26.320 --> 35:26.960
What?

35:27.920 --> 35:29.630
You mean my only strengths

35:29.630 --> 35:31.550
are prediction and a "cheat code"?

35:31.550 --> 35:32.360
Of course not.

35:33.510 --> 35:35.000
I mean,

35:35.550 --> 35:36.480
that's just

35:36.840 --> 35:38.710
your smallest strength.

35:39.590 --> 35:41.000
You have so many,

35:41.000 --> 35:42.360
so many other strengths.

35:42.360 --> 35:43.490
But only I know them.

35:43.570 --> 35:44.260
Really?

35:44.760 --> 35:46.070
Well, if you don't list

35:46.070 --> 35:47.400
at least five right now,

35:47.590 --> 35:48.650
I'll throw you off.

35:50.360 --> 35:51.220
Then I'll do it.

35:51.480 --> 35:54.510
Here—one, two, three, four, five.

35:55.400 --> 35:55.880
Down you go.

35:55.880 --> 35:56.810
[Asia's No. 1—Shengcheng
Chengrong Electronics City Plaza—]

35:56.810 --> 35:57.740
[50 Days to Grand Opening]

36:02.350 --> 36:04.180
Back when we opened Luna,

36:03.970 --> 36:07.980
[Luna]

36:04.360 --> 36:05.230
we had no money.

36:05.550 --> 36:07.000
Otherwise, I would've run an ad
like this too—

36:07.000 --> 36:07.860
30 days in a row.

36:08.320 --> 36:09.150
Luna's ads cost

36:09.150 --> 36:10.670
far more than this, okay?

36:11.630 --> 36:12.230
By the way,

36:12.440 --> 36:13.840
do you still remember Mr. Duan?

36:13.840 --> 36:15.070
He used to be in clothing,

36:15.070 --> 36:16.550
then switched to electronics.

36:16.550 --> 36:17.600
He asked me to find out

36:17.600 --> 36:18.920
how much the stalls in Electronics City

36:18.920 --> 36:19.850
are selling for.

36:20.040 --> 36:20.960
Rent only, not for sale.

36:20.960 --> 36:22.150
If you sign now,

36:22.150 --> 36:23.840
you get three years of usage rights.

36:23.840 --> 36:25.190
He needs to hurry if he wants one.

36:25.190 --> 36:26.190
The prime spots in the first batch

36:26.190 --> 36:27.140
have already been snapped up.

36:27.140 --> 36:28.670
And there aren't many left.

36:28.930 --> 36:29.810
Really?

36:29.840 --> 36:31.230
Your stalls are that popular?

36:31.230 --> 36:32.760
When have I ever lied to you?

36:38.760 --> 36:39.550
Hurry up!

36:41.360 --> 36:42.510
So slow!

36:42.020 --> 36:43.290
[Chengrong Electronics City—
Prime Stalls Now Open for Leasing]

36:45.840 --> 36:47.230
Do you even know the rules?

36:47.230 --> 36:48.150
Get to the back of the line!

36:48.150 --> 36:49.110
Miss, can I squeeze in?

36:49.110 --> 36:50.150
No cuts!

36:50.280 --> 36:51.360
The mall is so big,

36:51.360 --> 36:53.480
and there are so many stalls!
They won't run out!

36:53.480 --> 36:54.550
With so many stalls,

36:54.550 --> 36:55.590
why not release them all at once?

36:55.590 --> 36:56.960
Why split them into three batches?

36:56.960 --> 36:57.630
I wonder which

36:57.630 --> 36:59.360
wicked bastard came up
with this dirty trick!

36:59.360 --> 37:00.230
Can you hurry up?

37:00.230 --> 37:00.710
Exactly!

37:00.710 --> 37:02.370
What's wrong with you people?

37:02.760 --> 37:03.670
The annual rent

37:03.670 --> 37:04.710
will bring in seven million,

37:04.710 --> 37:06.360
and it takes up such a huge area.

37:06.360 --> 37:07.840
It'll keep generating profit

37:07.840 --> 37:08.970
for decades to come.

37:09.930 --> 37:10.880
How can that Brat Ji

37:10.880 --> 37:11.940
even compare to me?

37:12.110 --> 37:13.630
If everything goes smoothly

37:13.630 --> 37:15.150
and continues like this,

37:15.320 --> 37:17.650
the Second Master Du might actually lose.

37:17.960 --> 37:19.170
There's only one month left.

37:19.170 --> 37:21.230
How is he supposed to turn the tables?

37:21.400 --> 37:22.130
Xia Xiaolan,

37:22.230 --> 37:22.920
do you know what people here

37:22.920 --> 37:24.120
are saying about you?

37:24.770 --> 37:25.330
They say,

37:25.360 --> 37:26.380
"Which wicked bastard came up with

37:26.380 --> 37:28.640
this dirty trick?"

37:31.510 --> 37:32.280
Du Zhaohui,

37:32.630 --> 37:33.920
right now, you look just like

37:33.920 --> 37:35.190
those villains in the movies.

37:35.190 --> 37:36.720
Don't say I didn't warn you—

37:36.960 --> 37:38.190
villains always die

37:38.190 --> 37:39.510
because they celebrate too early.

37:39.510 --> 37:40.920
Never mind
that there's still a month left—

37:40.920 --> 37:42.410
even if there were only one day left,

37:42.410 --> 37:43.150
as long as Du Chengrong

37:43.150 --> 37:44.360
hasn't announced the winner,

37:44.360 --> 37:45.190
Du Zhaoji

37:45.480 --> 37:47.610
still has a chance to turn this around.

37:48.030 --> 37:49.440
I'd like to see him try.

37:49.870 --> 37:51.200
Don't worry. It's fine.

37:57.030 --> 37:57.440
Hello?

38:02.070 --> 38:02.630
Where did this man, Nie Weiguo,

38:02.630 --> 38:03.510
come from?

38:04.880 --> 38:07.440
He's claiming that our Electronics City
design copied his work!

38:07.440 --> 38:08.710
Judging by the lawyer's letter,

38:08.710 --> 38:09.970
that is what he thinks.

38:10.320 --> 38:11.250
What do you mean?

38:11.670 --> 38:12.590
Is there more to it

38:12.590 --> 38:13.650
beyond the letter?

38:14.000 --> 38:15.800
Everything requires evidence.

38:16.280 --> 38:17.110
For example, if I draw

38:17.110 --> 38:18.370
a colored apple first,

38:18.400 --> 38:19.110
and then you draw one,

38:19.110 --> 38:20.320
that's you copying me.

38:20.320 --> 38:21.980
But if the timeline is unclear

38:22.110 --> 38:23.760
and you run over, claiming I copied you,

38:23.760 --> 38:25.490
people might still believe it.

38:25.840 --> 38:28.000
We're done for. We're done for.

38:28.280 --> 38:29.810
Stop saying we're done for.

38:29.880 --> 38:30.880
It's my own work.

38:31.150 --> 38:33.460
I know perfectly well
whether I copied or not.

38:33.460 --> 38:35.910
The key is the timeline.

38:36.190 --> 38:37.880
Nie Weiguo claims

38:38.150 --> 38:39.630
that Hou Qi saw

38:39.630 --> 38:41.630
his unpublished design drawings.

38:42.230 --> 38:42.590
Me?

38:42.840 --> 38:43.510
How is that possible?

38:43.510 --> 38:44.550
I left Jiangcheng Design Institute

38:44.550 --> 38:45.440
ages ago!

38:49.710 --> 38:51.170
Hou Qi, come here for a sec.

39:01.480 --> 39:02.710
Is it really this woman?

39:02.710 --> 39:03.440
Impossible.

39:03.710 --> 39:05.510
Ms. Hou Qi isn't that kind of person.

39:05.510 --> 39:05.960
Wait,

39:06.190 --> 39:07.190
weren't most of the exterior designs

39:07.190 --> 39:08.110
Ms. Xia's work?

39:08.360 --> 39:09.070
What does this have to do

39:09.070 --> 39:09.930
with Ms. Hou Qi?

39:10.110 --> 39:11.240
What are you saying?

39:11.440 --> 39:13.030
How could Ms. Xia possibly plagiarize?

39:13.030 --> 39:13.440
Yeah.

39:14.000 --> 39:14.550
Ms. Xia,

39:14.950 --> 39:17.210
I swear I absolutely did not plagiarize.

39:17.440 --> 39:18.170
Don't worry.

39:18.550 --> 39:19.950
Of course, I believe you.

39:20.150 --> 39:21.280
I just want to ask—

39:21.280 --> 39:22.760
what kind of person is

39:22.760 --> 39:23.890
Nie Weiguo exactly?

39:26.960 --> 39:27.880
That guy, Nie,

39:28.650 --> 39:29.500
is a scumbag.

39:31.000 --> 39:32.530
Back then, he stole my work,

39:33.000 --> 39:34.260
exploited my labor...

39:35.430 --> 39:36.960
and even got handsy with me.

39:37.480 --> 39:38.670
I couldn't take it anymore,

39:38.670 --> 39:39.630
and that's why I quit

39:39.630 --> 39:41.090
and even left Jiangcheng.

39:41.750 --> 39:42.510
I can't believe this guy

39:42.510 --> 39:44.510
is getting more and more shameless.

39:46.840 --> 39:47.900
I'm sorry, Ms. Xia.

39:48.920 --> 39:49.780
No matter what,

39:50.440 --> 39:51.190
this trouble started

39:51.190 --> 39:52.000
because of me.

39:52.590 --> 39:53.590
Bad people do bad things.

39:53.590 --> 39:55.110
What does this have to do with you?

39:55.110 --> 39:55.880
Don't try to take it all

39:55.880 --> 39:56.920
upon yourself.

39:57.360 --> 39:58.220
Attorney Zhou,

39:58.590 --> 40:00.800
you can't just
accuse someone of plagiarism, right?

40:00.800 --> 40:03.030
Surely the law needs something
to go on, right?

40:03.030 --> 40:03.830
The evidence.

40:04.140 --> 40:04.940
Do we have any?

40:05.030 --> 40:05.440
Yes.

40:06.670 --> 40:07.630
But...

40:08.280 --> 40:09.110
But what?

40:10.360 --> 40:12.360
Is this going to be a tough case?

40:13.190 --> 40:14.280
The fact that Nie Weiguo

40:14.280 --> 40:15.070
has made this public

40:15.070 --> 40:17.000
shows he won't let it drop quietly.

40:17.440 --> 40:18.280
He's just a deputy director

40:18.280 --> 40:20.190
at a small design institute—

40:20.510 --> 40:22.170
what kind of waves can he make?

40:22.880 --> 40:24.030
I'll figure something out

40:24.030 --> 40:25.160
and make some calls.

40:25.670 --> 40:27.200
Get back to work, everyone.

40:29.400 --> 40:30.960
I'm certain this whole thing

40:30.960 --> 40:31.670
was cooked up

40:31.670 --> 40:32.880
by that Brat Ji!

40:33.360 --> 40:34.550
That darn bastard!

40:36.630 --> 40:38.670
Du Zhaohui thinks

40:38.670 --> 40:40.000
Du Zhaoji is behind this

40:40.030 --> 40:41.490
and that it's aimed at him.

40:42.190 --> 40:43.190
What do you think?

40:43.920 --> 40:45.030
For now,

40:45.840 --> 40:47.040
it does look that way.

40:47.590 --> 40:48.230
But...

40:49.030 --> 40:50.760
But something still feels off.

40:50.780 --> 40:52.730
Even though Chengrong Group

40:52.760 --> 40:53.840
will be affected,

40:54.150 --> 40:55.410
the biggest victim...

40:55.960 --> 40:56.820
is actually me.

40:57.880 --> 40:59.340
Then that can only mean...

40:59.630 --> 41:01.030
Xia Ziyu is involved too.

41:02.560 --> 41:04.510
But whether it's Du Zhaoji

41:04.510 --> 41:05.710
or Xia Ziyu,

41:06.440 --> 41:07.280
don't you think they seem to know you

41:07.280 --> 41:08.010
far too well?

41:08.920 --> 41:10.070
Your grudge with Nie Weiguo

41:10.070 --> 41:11.880
started as recently as

41:11.880 --> 41:13.190
the Jiangcheng Architecture Symposium.

41:13.190 --> 41:14.630
Even an enemy this far away,

41:14.630 --> 41:16.710
and yet they still managed to
track him down through Hou Qi.

41:16.710 --> 41:17.670
Unless...

41:20.280 --> 41:22.150
Unless there is a mole close to me.

41:30.840 --> 41:32.040
Who do you think it is?

41:32.550 --> 41:33.110
Hou Qi?

41:33.840 --> 41:34.700
It can't be her.

41:34.920 --> 41:36.030
Before Nie Weiguo and I

41:36.030 --> 41:37.150
even crossed paths,

41:37.150 --> 41:38.000
she had already left

41:38.000 --> 41:39.040
the Jiangcheng Design Institute.

41:39.040 --> 41:39.560
It shows

41:39.590 --> 41:41.050
that she did resign for personal reasons

41:41.050 --> 41:43.380
and had nothing to do
with what came after.

41:43.760 --> 41:45.220
Then who do you think it is?

41:45.840 --> 41:47.300
You should be able to guess

41:47.630 --> 41:48.760
who I'm thinking of.

41:54.630 --> 41:55.510
But he...

41:56.940 --> 41:57.920
hasn't shown anything unusual lately.

41:57.920 --> 41:58.340
True.

41:59.320 --> 42:00.150
We don't have

42:00.150 --> 42:01.880
any concrete evidence at the moment.

42:01.880 --> 42:04.030
But regarding the incident
at the symposium

42:04.030 --> 42:05.320
and Hou Qi's situation,

42:05.320 --> 42:07.050
he's the one who knows the most.

42:07.960 --> 42:09.630
Personally, I don't want to believe

42:09.630 --> 42:10.360
he could betray us

42:10.360 --> 42:11.440
like that.

42:12.070 --> 42:13.930
So let's just wait and see for now.

42:16.070 --> 42:17.710
What worries me most is—

42:18.190 --> 42:19.230
if Xia Ziyu really

42:19.670 --> 42:20.880
is behind all this,

42:21.360 --> 42:21.960
there will

42:22.190 --> 42:23.070
almost certainly be

42:23.070 --> 42:24.530
more dirty tricks to come.

42:25.400 --> 42:26.550
I think the color of the section

42:26.550 --> 42:27.920
could be brighter.

42:28.000 --> 42:28.920
To make it stand out more.

42:28.920 --> 42:29.280
Okay.

42:29.300 --> 42:29.760
Listen,

42:29.880 --> 42:30.760
go find Hou Qi.

42:30.960 --> 42:32.000
I talked to her about it yesterday.

42:32.000 --> 42:32.360
Okay.

42:35.070 --> 42:35.530
Ms. Xia.

42:37.250 --> 42:38.620
Director Pan,
the one who approved the loan

42:38.620 --> 42:39.150
for our Golden Sands Pool project,

42:39.150 --> 42:40.400
has been called in by the head branch
for questioning.

42:40.400 --> 42:42.400
The bank might ask us to repay early.

42:42.590 --> 42:43.120
Let's go.

42:43.280 --> 42:43.920
Let's go find my uncle.

42:43.920 --> 42:44.280
Okay.

42:46.550 --> 42:47.480
Look, look, look!

42:47.480 --> 42:48.510
Look at this lobby!

42:48.510 --> 42:49.370
Isn't it great?

42:49.710 --> 42:51.190
After today's inspection,

42:51.190 --> 42:51.920
can we

42:51.920 --> 42:53.380
settle the final payment?

42:58.360 --> 42:59.360
This tree here...

43:00.160 --> 43:02.370
This was just transplanted here.

43:02.400 --> 43:03.070
The landscapers

43:03.070 --> 43:04.590
haven't had time to prune it yet.

43:04.590 --> 43:06.510
So the landscaping work
won't be included in the inspection?

43:06.510 --> 43:06.910
No, no.

43:07.150 --> 43:08.670
They'll be here to prune it soon.

43:08.670 --> 43:09.230
Mr. Liu,

43:09.440 --> 43:10.440
look at these details.

43:10.440 --> 43:11.320
There are problems everywhere.

43:11.320 --> 43:12.520
Hurry up and fix them.

43:12.840 --> 43:13.640
I know, I know.

43:13.880 --> 43:14.230
But...

43:14.230 --> 43:15.190
Then the final payment

43:15.190 --> 43:16.400
will still need to
be settled today, right?

43:16.400 --> 43:16.860
Mr. Liu,

43:17.150 --> 43:17.880
don't worry.

43:18.320 --> 43:19.510
Once the inspection passes,

43:19.510 --> 43:21.040
we will definitely pay you.

43:21.510 --> 43:21.970
Wait...

43:22.630 --> 43:23.430
You aren't...

43:31.510 --> 43:32.040
Xiaolan!

43:32.870 --> 43:34.600
-What brings you here?
-Uncle.

43:35.440 --> 43:36.920
The one handling our bank loan,

43:36.920 --> 43:37.550
Director Pan,

43:37.550 --> 43:38.630
has been called in for questioning.

43:38.630 --> 43:39.320
There wasn't anything irregular

43:39.320 --> 43:40.090
in the loan process, right?

43:40.090 --> 43:41.950
The process was entirely proper.

43:43.110 --> 43:44.630
Is everything going smoothly here?

43:44.630 --> 43:45.440
Mr. Huo

43:45.440 --> 43:46.840
was supposed to do the inspection today.

43:46.840 --> 43:47.590
But he said

43:47.710 --> 43:49.630
something came up
and left on a business trip.

43:49.630 --> 43:50.710
Isn't it obvious he's just trying to

43:50.710 --> 43:52.640
avoid settling our final payment?

43:52.710 --> 43:53.480
I was thinking,

43:53.480 --> 43:54.230
since you're short on money now,

43:54.230 --> 43:54.920
this payment would

43:54.920 --> 43:56.380
at least ease things a bit.

44:02.550 --> 44:03.000
Hello?

44:07.280 --> 44:08.760
Okay, I got it. I'll be right there.
